    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Rise and shine! Before you begin\u2026</strong></p><p>Skim through these steps and get all your equipment ready, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Once done, simply dig in!</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/poached-egg-and-sriracha-hollandaise-pancake-stack/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/poached-egg-and-sriracha-hollandaise-pancake-stack/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large-wide based pan (preferably non stick) with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/poached-egg-and-sriracha-hollandaise-pancake-stack/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once fragrant, add the spinach, cook for 2-3 min or until lightly wilted \u2013 this is your <strong>garlic butter spinach</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/poached-egg-and-sriracha-hollandaise-pancake-stack/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Bring a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> gently into the water and leave them for 3 min</p><p>Once done, gently transfer the egg[s] with a slotted spoon to kitchen paper or a clean tea-towel and season them with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>poached egg[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/poached-egg-and-sriracha-hollandaise-pancake-stack/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add a generous knob of <strong>butter</strong> to a heatproof bowl and put in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 20 secs or until melted</p><p>Once melted, add your <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong> sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Stir it all together until you have a thick sauce<strong> </strong>\u2013<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>sriracha hollandaise</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/poached-egg-and-sriracha-hollandaise-pancake-stack/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>buttermilk pancakes</strong> to a plate and pop in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 30 secs on high or until warmed through</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/poached-egg-and-sriracha-hollandaise-pancake-stack/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>To build your pancake stack, spread some of the <strong>sriracha hollandaise </strong>on one of the <strong>pancakes</strong>, top with some of the <strong>garlic butter spinach </strong>and repeat until you have a stack of three pancakes per person</p><p>Top with a <strong>poached egg </strong>and the <strong>remaining sriracha hollandaise</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped chives</strong></p><p>Time to start your day!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
